Manual execution:

bash renewalsslcertificates.sh --email info@example.com --webroot /var/www/ --domain example.com

Via crontab:

#update certificates for websites
1 0 1 * * /var/script/bash renewalsslcertificates.sh --email info@example.com --webroot /var/www/ --domain example.com > /dev/null 2>&1
